*ngSwitch--

NgSwitch ek structural directive hai. jisme hum condition base data ko show krate hai ya perform
Nt:NgSwitch kis bhi trike ki value ko use kr leta hai and agr koi case match nhi hua to hum default ko use krte hai

1.ngSwitch kaisath Star nhi lgta hai kyoki yai expression ko bind krta hai jo result provide krta hai.
2.ngSwitchCase mai Starlgta hai kyki isme case match hota hai
3.ngSwitchDefault mai Starlgta hai kyki isme case match hota hai
4.Yai case sensitive hota hai
4.Isme brack ka use nhi krte hai